3. Model Adapter and Weights

The model adapter files under models/judge/ are LoRA/PEFT adapter artifacts
trained from the base model:

unsloth/Llama-3.2-1B-Instruct-bnb-4bit

Use of the adapter may require compliance with the license and acceptable use
terms of the underlying base model and any upstream model provider. Users are
responsible for reviewing and complying with the applicable upstream license
terms before using or redistributing the adapter.

